    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras/90f9ddc3be5be39d447696d2341973cb.avif?t=1763678679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras_big/90f9ddc3be5be39d447696d2341973cb.avif?t=1763678679 width=800 height=454 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to A Beautiful Collection of Darkness: Volume 2 - The Raven!<strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is the 2nd Volume in our new series - <u>A Beautiful Collection of Darkness</u>. You can find our other volumes on Steam!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In this Full Album + Art Pack, explore a grim, dark, heart-pounding musical experience created by Randumb Studios.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rediscover Edgar Allan Poe's &quot;The Raven&quot; in this beautifully crafted retelling of a timeless classic in ways that you've never experienced before!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras/60157f06ba6dd4dbfc6dc64fcf504bec.avif?t=1763678679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras_big/60157f06ba6dd4dbfc6dc64fcf504bec.avif?t=1763678679 width=800 height=532 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Featured in Volume 2 are nearly two-dozen absolute BANGERS, Full Lyrics, and a neat digital artbook to match! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>(Files come in standard MP3 format with optional download of WAV, FLAC, &amp; OGG.)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras/9d1ca3e02df18a5a1fa591a83ce45ae3.avif?t=1763678679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras_big/9d1ca3e02df18a5a1fa591a83ce45ae3.avif?t=1763678679 width=800 height=532 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thank you so much for choosing to support us in our journey while rocking out to tasty jams! It really means the world to us and we appreciate you more than words can express! ♥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras/43afc125956835b02b6b38e5cedec1ec.avif?t=1763678679\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226440/extras_big/43afc125956835b02b6b38e5cedec1ec.avif?t=1763678679 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Randumb Studios</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>We don't make games, we make experiences.</i></strong></p></li></ul>",
